Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.24,0:06:25.61,Default,,0,0,0,,谢谢…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.24,0:06:29.52,Default,,0,0,0,,坐霸王车是犯罪
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.65,0:06:33.19,Default,,0,0,0,,请问在哪里刷卡
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.54,0:06:34.27,Default,,0,0,0,,现金
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.96,0:06:36.40,Default,,0,0,0,,明码标价
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.66,0:06:38.28,Default,,0,0,0,,现金是什么
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.52,0:06:39.33,Default,,0,0,0,,犯罪
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.73,0:06:50.45,Default,,0,0,0,,用这个可以吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.92,0:06:53.47,Default,,0,0,0,,多谢惠顾
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.93,0:07:19.79,Default,,0,0,0,,这是哪里
